title: Green Curry Vegetable Soup
summary: If you want to add more dairy free and lacto ovo vegetarian recipes to your recipe box, Green Curry Vegetable Soup might be a recipe you should try. One serving contains 270 calories, 17g of protein, and 5g of fat. This recipe serves 1 and costs $2.28 per serving. This recipe is liked by 74 foodies and cooks. It works best as a main course, and is done in approximately 15 minutes. This recipe from Eating Well requires baby spinach, thai curry paste, angel hair pasta, and bell pepper. This recipe is typical of Indian cuisine. Autumn will be even more special with this recipe. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 100%. This score is super. Green Curry Vegetable Soup, spring vegetable thai green curry (with homemade curry paste!!), and Vegetable Green Curry are very similar to this recipe.
